Cozy Cotton Split Corner Bed Skirt 39x80 Rust Brown

USD33.28
Cozy Cotton offers a high-quality, fade-resistant 39 x 80 inch split corner bed skirt in rust brown. Made from 1000 Thread Count Egyptian Cotton, it hides bed frames and provides extra storage while being easy to clean and durable.
  • Description
  • Reviews

  This elegant Rust Brown Split Corner Bed Skirt adds a touch of sophistication and comfort to your bedroom. Crafted from high-quality 1000 Thread Count Egyptian Cotton, it ensures a soft and smooth feel while being wrinkle-resistant and durable. Its 3-sided construction conceals your bed frame and box spring, providing a polished appearance that elevates your bed set. The fade-resistant feature allows it to maintain its vibrant color for years, making it a stylish and long-lasting addition to your home decor.
  Perfect for Twin XL beds, this 39 x 80 inch bed skirt is designed to be both functional and practical. It not only hides the legs and frame of your bed but also creates extra storage space underneath, making it a versatile piece for your room. The easy-care qualities of this cotton bed skirt make maintenance a breeze—just machine wash and tumble dry. Ideal for those seeking an affordable yet luxurious upgrade to their bedding setup.
